{"tid":1164161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙中線大圍至鑽石山或局部通車 傳下月全面試車","createTime":"2019-05-21T01:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T12:57:02.000Z","uid":56881,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d9c2002c671e49db460d7b9073d34a348ce763cf","tid":1164161,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:27:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B7%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E8%87%B3%E9%91%BD%E7%9F%B3%E5%B1%B1%E6%88%96%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A-%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E8%A9%A6%E8%BB%8A-151600704.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258D%25E8%2587%25B3%25E9%2591%25BD%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E8%25BB%258A-151600704.html&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=0c33a464\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B7%9A%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E8%87%B3%E9%91%BD%E7%9F%B3%E5%B1%B1%E6%88%96%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A-%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E8%A9%A6%E8%BB%8A-151600704.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YTRLXe6MOMyTwSi_ayv4iw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190520a232855.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FYTRLXe6MOMyTwSi_ayv4iw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190520a232855.jpg&h=71f07ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙中線傳局部通車，但列車會「飛過」啟德及宋皇臺兩站。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】本來預料於今年年中通車的沙中綫工程大圍至紅磡段，因紅磡站工程問題而一直未知可否全線或局部通車，今日有消息指港鐵初步決定先開通大圍至鑽石山段，但鑽石山至土瓜灣兩站亦會設立有限度的「穿梭列車」服務，但1小時可能只有數班車，而為實施上述計劃，有關路段將於下月起全面試車，當試車超過約2個月，有足夠的測試數據，或就可局部通車。不過，以上安排下，列車將會「飛過」啟德及宋皇臺兩站，消息就指是因該兩站仍有基建未完成。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵就沒有正面回應試車消息，只表示沙中綫全綫或局部開通，要視乎紅磡站及相連結構的核實情況，有關範圍已納入調查委員會進一步的調查，而屯馬綫其他車站記錄的核實工作亦進行中。此外，港鐵亦需要考慮一連串包括改動信號系統等技術因素，因此，就開通時間以至局部開通與否，現時暫未能有所定論。<br />\n<br />\n通左車當無數?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f987bd00f5d9ab11f2c7d9558ef5175f433ad3d7","tid":1164161,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:28:59.000Z","msg":"屌 通得兩個話 即係塞撚爆鑽石山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343585240fabd31d0432b688cf5b4159acee9a38","tid":1164161,"uid":41308,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:32:12.000Z","msg":"呢段通車<br />\n亦都係東鐵變九卡<br />\n<br />\n東鐵一定日日大混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86451f7a5bf37370ca7e21b343499c59acb85f7f","tid":1164161,"uid":50862,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"343585240fabd31d0432b688cf5b4159acee9a38","tid":1164161,"uid":41308,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:32:12.000Z","msg":"呢段通車<br />\n亦都係東鐵變九卡<br />\n<br />\n東鐵一定日日大混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:36:44.000Z","msg":"呢段通車東鐵唔洗變九卡<br />\n紅磡過海果段先係令東鐵變九卡既原因<br />\n大圍鑽石山呢段可以當係馬鐵延線咁睇"},{"pid":"e8a274cc8b2d1b640e6b47f3e5aa05d5094ff727","tid":1164161,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:43:53.000Z","msg":"快啲通車啦 九龍塘好撚多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db781135226aa085b50a90c125282ca0deb6ff0c","tid":1164161,"uid":41308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"q